```sql
WITH monthly_sales_by_category AS (
  SELECT
    DATE_TRUNC(CAST(t1.created_at AS DATE), MONTH) AS sales_month,
    t2.category,
    SUM(t1.sale_price) AS total_sales
  FROM
    `thelook_ecommerce.order_items` AS t1
    JOIN `thelook_ecommerce.products` AS t2 ON t1.product_id = t2.id
  GROUP BY
    1,
    2
), monthly_growth AS (
  SELECT
    sales_month,
    category,
    total_sales,
    LAG(total_sales, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY category ORDER BY sales_month) AS previous_month_sales
  FROM
    monthly_sales_by_category
)
SELECT
  monthly_growth.sales_month,
  monthly_growth.category,
  (monthly_growth.total_sales - monthly_growth.previous_month_sales) / monthly_growth.previous_month_sales AS growth_rate
FROM
  monthly_growth
WHERE
  monthly_growth.previous_month_sales IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  monthly_growth.category,
  monthly_growth.sales_month
```
